      <title>Lululemon 警告北美销售因支出下滑而放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/lululemon-sees-annual-revenue-below-estimates-weaker-demand-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lululemon Athletica 周四预测年度收入和利润低于预期，原因是该服装零售商主要在北美地区的高端运动休闲需求减弱，导致其股价在盘后交易中下跌近 11%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/lululemon-sees-annual-revenue-below-estimates-weaker-demand-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 20:17:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FTX预计美国破产索赔额将减少至30亿至50亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ftx-expects-us-reduce-bankruptcy-claim-3-billion-5-billion-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币交易所 FTX 表示，预计将通过谈判将美国政府的破产索赔额降至 30 亿至 50 亿美元，这样股东就不会剩下任何钱，这与创始人 Sam Bankman-Fried 声称 FTX 的倒闭没有造成任何损害的“鲁莽且虚假”的说法相矛盾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ftx-expects-us-reduce-bankruptcy-claim-3-billion-5-billion-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 19:48:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
